lyrics.og: It might not be the right time
I might not be the right one
But there's something about us I want to say
lyrics.zh: 但有些我們之間的事，我想說說
反正我們之間本來就有些什麼

lyrics.og: I might not be the right one
It might not be the right time
But there's something about us I've got to do
lyrics.zh: 但有些我們之間的事，我必須做

lyrics.og: Some kind of secret I will share with you
lyrics.zh: 我想和妳分享某個秘密

lyrics.og: I need you more than anything in my life
lyrics.zh: 比起我人生中的其他一切，我更需要妳

lyrics.og: I want you more than anything in my life
lyrics.zh: 比起我人生中的其他一切，我更想要妳

lyrics.og: I'll miss you more than anyone in my life
lyrics.zh: 比起我生命中的其他人，我會更想念妳

lyrics.og: I love you more than anyone in my life
lyrics.zh: 比起我生命中的其他人，我更愛妳
